  "remarks": "\n The Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that Seyed Majid Feiz JAFARI is an involved person under The Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 on the basis of the following ground: JAFARI is or has been responsible for activity which amounts to a serious human rights violation or abuse in Iran, namely the right to freedom of expression and peaceful assembly.\n",
